{
    "name": "Sailor (First Mate)",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "A first mate is the loyal assistant to a ship\u2019s captain. He oversees duties and discipline aboard ship, feared but always respected; he is able to entertain with a sea shanty one moment and ply his trusty lash or flashing cutlasses the next. A first mate could also be the warden of an exotic island prison. Away from their ships, first mates can be found with a traveling merchant quartermaster (CR 9), or a captain (CR 12)."
        }
    ],
